{"TopicId":171984,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Ann Gillis - 2001: A Space Odyssey","CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-11T07:31:22Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-11T07:31:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile looking for something else, I just ran across the news that \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ann_Gillis\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EAnn Gillis\u003C/a\u003E, who played Dr. Frank Poole\u0027s mother in the Kubrik / Clarke film \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2001:_A_Space_Odyssey_(film)\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E2001: A Space Odyssey\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E, had recently died... without any fanfare in the press apparently, not that I saw. She passed away on January 31, 2018. RIP\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alan_Gifford\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EAlan Gifford (John Lennox)\u003C/a\u003E, who played the role as Poole\u0027s father, passed years earlier on March 20, 1989.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cratercracker","CreatedById":171449,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-11T11:09:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s sad. Thanks for letting us know though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;.;\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cry.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;.;\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}